spec: agent-core.ai-docs/v1
namespace: "Infrastructure\\Storage"
fqcn: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Infrastructure\\Storage"
updatedAt: 2026-04-22
description: "Storage adapters — in-memory stores, Flysystem run logs, Doctrine event store, hot prompt state, local artifact store."
files[10]{file,type,summary}:
  HotPromptStateStore.php,final class,Caches prompt execution state in memory keyed by run ID for high-speed access during active agent runs.
  InMemoryCommandStore.php,final class,"Manages pending commands in memory with idempotent enqueue and state transitions (applied, rejected, superseded) per run."
  InMemoryOutboxStore.php,final class,Buffers outbox entries in memory with sink-based deduplication for domain event publication.
  InMemoryPromptStateStore.php,final class,Stores prompt state per run ID in an ephemeral in-memory array.
  InMemoryRunAccessStore.php,final class,"Holds run access scopes in memory, keyed by run ID."
  InMemoryRunStore.php,final class,Persists run states in memory with versioned optimistic locking for concurrent-update safety.
  LocalArtifactStore.php,readonly final class,"Persists artifacts to the local filesystem, organized by run ID and artifact name."
  RunEventStore.php,final class,"Stores run events in memory, supporting append and retrieval of the full event history per run."
  RunLogReader.php,readonly final class,"Reads run log files from the filesystem to reconstruct event sequences for a specific run. It parses JSON lines into domain events, providing a read-only view of historical run data."
  RunLogWriter.php,readonly final class,"Appends run events as JSON lines to Flysystem-backed log files, partitioned by run ID."